147
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:30,640
I can't get you tissue like this.

148
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,580
Go like this, then.

149
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:40,400
Put me down.

150
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,400
Well,

151
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:03,520
