158
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:31,780
Newspaper briefing, I guess.

159
00:07:32,180 --> 00:07:34,320
Sometimes, he collects something
he's interested in.

160
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,760
This thing...

161
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:42,020
It looks familiar.

162
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,840
Give me a pen and paper.

163
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,060
He Village?

164
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,940
I heard about this place.

165
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:25,080
In Huangping Town, I think.

166
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,720
(On the day of the car crash,)

167
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:33,360
(why was Grandpa carrying this map?)

168
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,350
