175
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:05,080
I have to take back the hard drive.

176
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,920
And all these...

177
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:12,760
I should take them back, too.

178
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:21,740
Old Chief raised me for 12 years.

179
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:23,820
He only told me

180
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,680
how he established Yunlu Abode.

181
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,400
He never talked about you.

182
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,880
He never mentioned you, either.

183
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:36,940
If...

184
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,880
If Old Chief was traveling

185
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,480
between two worlds,

186
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,720
can we be siblings?

187
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,440
What are you talking about?

188
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,780
I don't need a sister.

189
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:48,620
I need...

190
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,240
Need what?

191
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,460
Need...

192
00:09:53,190 --> 00:09:58,890
♪Time was a scale but later measured♪

193
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:04,870
♪Waiting seemed out of place♪

194
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:12,700
♪I couldn't say how much I missed you♪

195
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:18,130
♪Old memories would tell that though♪

196
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,990
♪I meant to ask if you♪

197
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:27,090
♪remembered the alarm code♪

198
00:10:27,890 --> 00:10:33,410
♪I wished to see you as the door opened♪

199
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:36,090
♪So, I didn't♪

200
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:41,450
♪change any furnishings♪

201
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:48,150
♪Were you back, you'd be more adaptable♪

202
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:54,880
♪There must be some way to find you♪

203
00:10:56,050 --> 00:11:01,420
